
  4-button Position Calculation Formula
-----------------------------------------

Button labels
TI: Top Inner
BI: Bottom Inner
TO: Top Outer
BO: Bottom Outer

Xcoeff = Horizontal button spacing distance
Ycoeff = Vertical button spacing distance

sum  = TI + BI + BO + TO
Xnum = TO + BO - BI - TI
Ynum = TO - BO - BI + TI

X_position = Xcoeff * (Xnum/sum)
Y_position = Ycoeff * (Ynum/sum)

			      ^
      TI=Card 0   TO=Card 3   | +Y
 IN
 <-
      BI=Card 1   BO=Card 2   +X
			      -->
